MODULE: dev-pipeline
FILES: run.sh, run-bugfix.sh, launch-daemon.sh, launch-bugfix-daemon.sh, retry-feature.sh
RESPONSIBILITY: Shell and Python scripts orchestrating AI CLI dev sessions for feature building and bugfix pipelines

SUBDIRS:
- scripts: Python orchestration (init-pipeline.py, init-dev-team.py, detect-stuck.py, utils.py, etc.)
- lib: Shell library (common.sh, heartbeat.sh)
- templates: Bootstrap prompts and JSON schemas (feature-list-schema.json, bug-fix-list-schema.json)
- assets: Integration docs and examples

INTERFACES:
- run.sh: main feature pipeline entry point
- run-bugfix.sh: bugfix pipeline entry point
- launch-daemon.sh: daemonized feature pipeline
- launch-bugfix-daemon.sh: daemonized bugfix pipeline
- retry-feature.sh: retry failed features

DEPENDENCIES:
- uses: Python 3: pipeline orchestration scripts
- uses: bash: shell wrappers and library
- uses: simple-git (via Node.js): git operations
- imports: src/pipeline-infra: Node.js pipeline infrastructure

UPDATED: 2026-03-16
